    {
      "segments": [
        {
          "scid": "an4.80:1.1",
          "pli": "Ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā kosambiyaṃ viharati ghositārāme. ",
          "en": "At one time the Buddha was staying near Kosambi, in Ghosita’s Monastery. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an4.80:1.2",
          "pli": "Atha kho āyasmā ānando yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. Ekamantaṃ nisinno kho āyasmā ānando bhagavantaṃ etadavoca: ",
          "en": "Then Venerable Ānanda went up to the Buddha, bowed, sat down to one side, and said to him: "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an4.80:2.1",
          "pli": "“Ko nu kho, bhante, hetu ko paccayo, yena mātugāmo neva sabhāyaṃ nisīdati, na kammantaṃ payojeti, na kambojaṃ gacchatī”ti? ",
          "en": "“Sir, what is the cause, what is the reason why females don’t attend council meetings, work for a living, or travel to Persia?” "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an4.80:2.2",
          "pli": "“Kodhano, ānanda, mātugāmo; ",
          "en": "“Ānanda, females are irritable, "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an4.80:2.3",
          "pli": "issukī, ānanda, mātugāmo; ",
          "en": "jealous, "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an4.80:2.4",
          "pli": "maccharī, ānanda, mātugāmo; ",
          "en": "stingy, "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an4.80:2.5",
          "pli": "duppañño, ānanda, mātugāmo—",
          "en": "and unintelligent. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an4.80:2.6",
          "pli": "ayaṃ kho, ānanda, hetu ayaṃ paccayo, yena mātugāmo neva sabhāyaṃ nisīdati, na kammantaṃ payojeti, na kambojaṃ gacchatī”ti. ",
          "en": "This is the cause, this is the reason why females don’t attend council meetings, work for a living, or travel to Persia.” "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an4.80:2.7",
          "pli": "Dasamaṃ. ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an4.80:2.8",
          "pli": "Apaṇṇakavaggo tatiyo. ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an4.80:3.1",
          "pli": "Padhānaṃ diṭṭhisappurisa, ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an4.80:3.2",
          "pli": "Vadhukā dve ca honti aggāni; ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an4.80:3.3",
          "pli": "Kusināraacinteyyā, ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an4.80:3.4",
          "pli": "Dakkhiṇā ca vaṇijjā kambojanti. ",
          "en": ""
        }
      ],
